  "description": {
    "en": {
      "provenance": "imported",
      "value": "Provide technical, financial logistic support to Rebuild and Retrofit/Repair Schools;\r\n\r\nProvide geotechnical and geomatics services, such as, 3-D mapping of affected VDCs, drone imaging, and geotechnical risk management and site safety guidelines for terrace construction;\r\n\r\nProvide structural engineering services and develop technical resources and guidelines for retrofitting and reconstruction (if possible, service to be provided inside NRA Technical Resource Center);\r\n\r\nProvide technical assistance for earthquake    resistant construction to partners, government agencies, communities, and families. (if possible, service to be provided inside NRA Technical Resource Center);\r\n\r\nDisseminate Disaster-resistant NRA approved awareness materials and other technical materials;\r\n\r\nProvide community awareness activities, such as presentations and theater, to engage and mobilize communities to build back safer. Advocate with stakeholders for inclusion of Build Back Safer materials and resources for reconstruction;\r\n\r\nProvide NRA approved mason training to local builders and partners; and provide on-the-job practical training with mobile training units;"
    },
    "ne": null
  },
